                  "text": "TemplateID",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " optimizes lookups and ensures efficient data retrieval. Given the table's simplicity, this indexing strategy is sufficient for expected operations."
