                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "CrystalReportPath",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is limited to 200 characters. If file paths exceed this length, it could lead to data truncation. Consider increasing the length if necessary."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Indexing",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": While the current indexing strategy is adequate, if the table grows significantly or if there are frequent queries based on "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "CrystalReportPath",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", consider adding a non-clustered index on this column."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Data Redundancy",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Ensure that the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Scheduler.ReportTemplate",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table is properly normalized to avoid redundancy and maintain data integrity across related tables."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Security",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Ensure that access to the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "CrystalReportPath",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is controlled to prevent unauthorized access to sensitive report templates."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Overall, the table is well-structured for its intended purpose, with clear relationships and constraints that support data integrity and performance."
        }
      ]
